ys system feedback, status changes or required action; throughout detailed, prominent, persistent and actionable","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"communication. Alert message includes functional icon and semantic colour, and may include as well a close button and\/or action link.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Alert Message does not disappear automatically and remains visible until dismissed or resolved by the user.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSAlertMessage","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSAlertMessage","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSInlineAlert":{"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSInlineAlert","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"OUDSInlineAlert","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Inline alert is a lightweight UI element, placed in the content flow, that displays information, system feedback,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"status changes throughout short, prominent, persistent and non actionable communication. Inline alert includes functional","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"icon and semantic colour, and does not include a close button and\/or action link. Inline alert does not disappear and remains visible.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSInlineAlert","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsinlinealert","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSInlineAlert","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents":{"role":"collection","title":"Components","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents","abstract":[{"text":"The catalog of all components provided by OUDS. It contains also ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeV